**Hello.**

* [Sharing (Bukkit Plugin)](http://dev.bukkit.org/bukkit-mods/sharing/)
* [StickySlimes (Bukkit Plugin)](http://dev.bukkit.org/bukkit-plugins/stickyslimes/)
* [Claymores (Bukkit Plugin)](http://dev.bukkit.org/bukkit-plugins/claymores/)
* [SquidBreed (Bukkit Plugin)](http://dev.bukkit.org/bukkit-plugins/squidbreed/) -- [Source Code](https://github.com/r3dsea/SquidBreed)
* [Ticks/Seconds Converter](https://github.com/r3dsea/Ticks-Seconds-Converter)

**Plugin Installation Tutorial:**

Steps:

1. Download all required files (below the "Steps")
1. Place the downloaded "Jython.jar" into the 'lib' folder of your server (if "lib" does not exist, please create it)
1. Place the "PyPluginLoader-versionX.jar" into the "plugin" folder of your server
1. Place downloaded ".pyp" file into the "plugin" folder

Downloads:

* [PythonPluginLoader](http://dev.bukkit.org/bukkit-mods/python-plugin-loader/|PythonPluginLoader) (PythonPluginLoader is compatible with current version of Bukkit, even if it doesn't say so)
* Jython: Link available on PythonPluginLoader page linked above (By downloading and using Jython you accept the [license](http://www.jython.org/license.html|the license))

That's all for now.
